<p>Stunt win: Eddie Perez wins Outstanding Stunt Coordination for a Comedy or Variety Program for Shameless</p>

<p>Best music: Labirinth wins Outstanding Original Music and Lyrics for All For Us from the Euphoria season finale And the Salt Of The Earth Behind You</p>
